<div><head>《周生烈子》</head>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1371_CHANT_001-1a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2a1371_CHANT_001-1a" ed="CHANT" n="001-1a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1371_CHANT_001-1a.2">天下所以平者，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1371_CHANT_001-1a.3">政平也。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1371_CHANT_001-1a.4">政所以平者，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1371_CHANT_001-1a.5">心平也。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1371_CHANT_001-1a.6">心所以平者，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1371_CHANT_001-1a.7">衡平也。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1371_CHANT_001-1a.8">衡所以平者，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1371_CHANT_001-1a.9">銖兩平也。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1371_CHANT_001-1a.10">銖兩所平者，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1371_CHANT_001-1a.11">毫釐平也。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1371_CHANT_001-1a.12">無所不均也，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1371_CHANT_001-1a.13">無所不平也，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1371_CHANT_001-1a.14">謂之太平。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1371_CHANT_001-1a.15">夫天之于物，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1371_CHANT_001-1a.16">無所偏以，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1371_CHANT_001-1a.17">君之散恩，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1371_CHANT_001-1a.18">無所內外。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1371_CHANT_001-1a.19">《太平御覽》。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1371_CHANT_001-2a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2a1371_CHANT_001-2a" ed="CHANT" n="001-2a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1371_CHANT_001-2a.2">心者眾智之門，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1371_CHANT_001-2a.3">要物皆求於心。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1371_CHANT_001-2a.4">《太平御覽》。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1371_CHANT_001-2a.5">口者言之門。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1371_CHANT_001-2a.6">《太平御覽》。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1371_CHANT_001-2a.7">夫忠謇朝之把扒，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1371_CHANT_001-2a.8">正人國之掃篲也，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1371_CHANT_001-2a.9">秉把執篲，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1371_CHANT_001-2a.10">除凶掃穢，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1371_CHANT_001-2a.11">國之福、主之利也。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1371_CHANT_001-2a.12">《太平御覽》。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1371_CHANT_001-3a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2a1371_CHANT_001-3a" ed="CHANT" n="001-3a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1371_CHANT_001-3a.2">舜嘗駕五龍以騰唐衢，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1371_CHANT_001-3a.3">武嘗服九駮以馳文塗，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1371_CHANT_001-3a.4">此上御也。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1371_CHANT_001-3a.5">《困學紀聞》。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1371_CHANT_001-3a.6">居堯舜之位而不行唐虞之政者，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1371_CHANT_001-3a.7">猶反衣狐白，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1371_CHANT_001-3a.8">步牽騄耳。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1371_CHANT_001-3a.9">《太平御覽》。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1371_CHANT_001-4a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2a1371_CHANT_001-4a" ed="CHANT" n="001-4a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1371_CHANT_001-4a.2">桀紂是湯武之梯，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1371_CHANT_001-4a.3">秦項是大漢之階也。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1371_CHANT_001-4a.4">四逆不興，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1371_CHANT_001-4a.5">則三順不勝。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1371_CHANT_001-4a.6">《太平御覽》。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1371_CHANT_001-4a.7">夫獵葉之風，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1371_CHANT_001-4a.8">不應八節。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1371_CHANT_001-4a.9">《太平御覽》。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1371_CHANT_001-5a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2a1371_CHANT_001-5a" ed="CHANT" n="001-5a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1371_CHANT_001-5a.2">行賞不洽，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1371_CHANT_001-5a.3">是春半生也；<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1371_CHANT_001-5a.4">行罰不威，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1371_CHANT_001-5a.5">是秋半死也。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1371_CHANT_001-5a.6">半生之春不洽于仁，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1371_CHANT_001-5a.7">半死之秋不專于義。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1371_CHANT_001-5a.8">《太平御覽》。<lb/></seg>
</p>
